title: Legend of Zelda - Hyrule Historia - Best version
description:
Hi everyone,

I wasn't happy with the way others have removed the Dark Horse watermarks from this PDF - all of the transparent objects in the PDF are either missing completely or totally opaque.

So I did it the right way and retained all the proper transparency. I've also added bookmarks, and the table of contents is properly hyperlinked. Compare any page in my version to the other version available on here and you'll clearly see a difference. 

Consider this version "archival."

Enjoy!
